<div class="block-contributor">
		

		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p>At the age of seventeen, <span class="smallcaps"><strong>Stephen J. Lyons</strong></span> won a trophy for four years of perfect attendance at Chicago&rsquo;s Mather High School. Now in his forties, he still believes, as Woody Allen said, that &ldquo;80 percent of success is showing up.&rdquo; He lives in Monticello, Illinois.</p><a href="/contributors/stephen-j-lyons" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
	</div>
